    public class EEFButtonDescriptionImpl
extends EEFWidgetDescriptionImpl
implements EEFButtonDescription
    An implementation of the model object 'EEF Button Description'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Button Label Expression
    • Image Expression
    • Push Expression
    • Style
    • Conditional Styles
